snippet.textDisplay:
This song is nice, yes.  However if you want to know why this song is beautiful and pierces the heart.  It because the song is about him.  About he, who if it were not for him, Allah would not have created the universe, the roses would have no fragrance, the mother would not have mercy towards her child.  He is like us but we are nothing like him, his face which outshines the moon, his sweat bead like musk, people would fight each other just to collect the water which falls from his blessed face.  This song is about Muhammad (may the peace and blessings of Allah be upon him).  The prophet of Muslims and the non Muslims, whether you accept or not.  No one will understand his value until the day of Resurrection  where we all run to him for protection. 

I love you ya Rasulullah.
